gc.pmb_library.android.internal.json
Class JsonParser

java.lang.Object
  gc.pmb_library.android.internal.json.JsonParser

public class JsonParser
extends java.lang.Object

The Class JsonParser.

Author:
Carsten Fasold
Copyright 2012 GrandCentrix GmbH.
All rights reserved.
This class will retrieve a list of where the tag or QuietTime model stored. It builds from this Models a JsonObject. Also it Receive a RegisterModel to build a JsonObject. Vice versa from a JSONobject a Tag- or QuietTimeobject. This JSONobject if used to send/receive JSON from the PushMeBabyServer.
